# failedCount

**Type**

The count of subscriptions that fail to receive a subscription-renewal-date extension.

## Declaration

```swift
int64 failedCount
```

## Discussion

For information about retrying a renewal date extension when if fails, see [doc://com.apple.appstoreserverapi/documentation/AppStoreServerAPI/extending-the-renewal-date-for-auto-renewable-subscriptions].

## Data types

- **complete**: A Boolean value that indicates whether the App Store completed the request to extend a subscription renewal date to active subscribers.
- **completeDate**: The UNIX time, in milliseconds, that the App Store completes a request to extend a subscription renewal date for eligible subscribers.
- **succeededCount**: The count of subscriptions that successfully receive a subscription-renewal-date extension.
